This film’s very interesting for person who love Japanese manga.
Ai, Mai, Mii, and Ponoka-sempai are girls in manga club. They’re fighting evil invaders threatening Earth, facing off against rivals in tournaments, and dealing with other absurd situations when they are not drawing manga. A excited story’s about the four-panel manga “Ai Mai Mi”.
